	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yamaha's clones of AY-3-8910 contain built-in source clock divider by 2. It is optional in YM2149, controlled with a pin; but seems to be always enabled for YMZ284.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
